          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic </strong></p>\n<p>Zest 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lemon </strong>and cut the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>in half</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
