    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften </p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
