            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained linguine</strong><strong> </strong>and<strong> broccoli</strong> to the pot with the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>and <strong>lemon zest</strong> </p>\n<p>Squeeze in the<strong> juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and add the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> </p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> Purple Sprouting Broccoli &amp; Lemon Linguine </strong></p>\n<p>Tip: add a drizzle more olive oil if your pasta is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
