            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into wedges</p>\n<p>Serve the <strong>Purple Sprouting Broccoli &amp; Lemon Linguine</strong> topped with the <strong>rocket</strong></p>\n<p>Sprinkle with the<strong> toasted pine nuts</strong>,<strong> </strong>then season with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong></p>\n<p>Garnish with a wedge of<strong> lemon </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
